'''台流'''（{{lang-ja|台流}}、{{lang-en|Taiwanese Wave}}）是[[日本|日本]]因為[[臺灣|臺灣]]的[[流行文化|流行文化]]普及所創造一個[[新詞|新詞]]，用於區分[[韓國|韓國]]的[[韓流|韓流]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cpopaccess.com/2010/02/rainie-yang-releases-japanese-version.html|title=Rainie Yang releases Japanese version of "Youth Bucket" that fans do want|last=Pauli|publisher=CpopAccess|date=2010-02-02|accessdate=2013-07-07|quote=The English-based Kpop blogosphere has made it known to western fans of the huge popularity of Kpop over in Japan, but what has not been reported is that Kpop is actually only one of two popular trends going on over in the land of the rising sun. The other trend, of course, is Taiwanese pop. We kid you not, and there’s even a word for it Japanese called '''台流''' (pronounced Tairyū), which literally means the influx of Taiwanese pop culture in Japan.|archive-date=2018-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180820234852/http://www.cpopaccess.com/2010/02/rainie-yang-releases-japanese-version.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。許多[[台灣電視劇|台灣電視劇]]及[[華語流行音樂|華語流行音樂]]在[[東亞|東亞]]及[[東南亞|東南亞]]流行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://dep.com.vn/han-hoa-ky-tich-tu-co-tich-danh-cho-nguoi-lon/|title=“HÀN HÓA” – KỲ TÍCH TỪ CỔ TÍCH DÀNH CHO NGƯỜI LỚN|author=Hoài Phạm|publisher=depweb|date=2014-04-21|accessdate=2019-06-14|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108211053/https://dep.com.vn/han-hoa-ky-tich-tu-co-tich-danh-cho-nguoi-lon/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==歷史==
21世紀初期，儘管[[韓流|韓流]]的早期成功，同為[[亞洲四小龍|亞洲四小龍]]的台灣，流行文化同樣明顯增長。2001年，台灣電視劇“[[流星花園_(台灣電視劇)|流星花園]]”的播出，很快吸引全國各地的觀眾。它成為[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]電視史上收視率最高的劇集<ref name="hollywoodasia">{{cite web|last=Celdran|first=David|title=It's Hip to Be Asian|url=http://pcij.org/imag/Society/asian.html|publisher=PHILIPPINE CENTER FOR INVESTIGATIVE JOURNALISM|accessdate=19 March 2013|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6FEqxHmvt?url=http://pcij.org/imag/Society/asian.html|archivedate=2013-03-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，囊括[[馬尼拉|馬尼拉]]超過10萬人次的觀眾<ref>{{cite web|last=Celdran|first=David|title=It's Hip to Be Asian|url=http://pcij.org/imag/Society/asian2.html|publisher=PHILIPPINE CENTER FOR INVESTIGATIVE JOURNALISM|accessdate=19 March 2013|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6FEqlbzDw?url=http://pcij.org/imag/Society/asian2.html|archivedate=2013-03-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，並且台灣男子組合[[F4_(台灣男子團體)|F4]]男主角們一夜成名<ref>{{cite web|last=Kee-yun|first=Tan|title=Welcome back pretty boys|url=http://news.asiaone.com/News/Latest%2BNews/Showbiz/Story/A1Story20130215-402353.html|publisher=[[Asiaone|Asiaone]]|accessdate=19 March 2013|archive-date=2018-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180525182222/http://news.asiaone.com/News/Latest%2BNews/Showbiz/Story/A1Story20130215-402353.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他們的知名度傳遍亞洲，包括[[中國|中國]]，[[香港|香港]]，[[新加坡|新加坡]]，[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]，[[泰國|泰國]]，[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]]，[[日本|日本]]，[[韓國|韓國]]，[[越南|越南]]和[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]。隨著他們的成功，其他台灣男孩團體一一出現，如[[5566|5566]]、[[183Club|183Club]]和[[飛輪海|飛輪海]]。 2002年，英國廣播公司[[BBC|BBC]]記者描述F4“激起整個亞洲的歇斯底里”<ref>{{cite web|last=Hewitt|first=Duncan|title=Taiwan 'boy band' rocks China|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/1998138.stm|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|accessdate=19 March 2013|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125214902/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/1998138.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

流星花園的成功可以歸因於以下兩個因素：
*主角間情感引起觀眾的情感投入
*引起女性觀眾慾望，由女性角度出發<ref>{{cite book|last=Ying Zhu|title=TV China|year=2009|publisher=[[Indiana_University_Press|Indiana University Press]]|pages=100}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Heryanto|first=Ariel|title=Popular Culture in Indonesia: Fluid Identities in Post-Authoritarian Politics|url=https://archive.org/details/popularculturein00hery|year=2008|publisher=[[Routledge|Routledge]]|pages=[https://archive.org/details/popularculturein00hery/page/n115 105]}}</ref>

2002年後，[[東南亞|東南亞]]地區電視節目的趨勢發生了很大變化，原本保留給[[好萊塢電影|好萊塢電影]]的黃金時段充滿了[[韓國電視劇|韓國]]和[[台灣電視劇|台灣電視劇]]<ref name="hollywoodasia"/>；韓國電視劇逐漸超越台灣，但大部分仍然聚焦在台灣團體，如F4、[[SHE|SHE]]和飛輪海等。

2000年代後期，許多台灣音樂已被[[韓流|韓流]]所超越；在國際上，雖然F4和飛輪海等台灣團體仍有小眾市場，但[[韓國流行音樂|韓國流行音樂]]的團體擁有更廣的客群，如[[BIGBANG|BIGBANG]]和[[Super_Junior|Super Junior]]。

